APPL JCTEST30

INVOKE 'SWS.ESP.APPL.PROCLIB(#DISTRIB)'

/********************************************************************/
/* 09/12/217 - TESTING GENTIMES FOR REPORTS FOR LAST MONTH
/********************************************************************/

AIX_JOB GENTIME_31_DAY_MONTH LINK PROCESS
   GENTIME PMFD FIRST DAY OF MONTH LESS 1 MONTH STARTING TODAY
   GENTIME PMLD LAST DAY OF MONTH LESS 1 MONTH STARTING TODAY
   ECHO !PMFDMM!PMFDDD!PMFDYEAR !PMLDMM!PMLDDD!PMLDYEAR
   RUN 3RD WORKDAY OF JAN MAR MAY JUL AUG OCT DEC
ENDJOB

AIX_JOB GENTIME_30_DAY_MONTHLINK PROCESS
   GENTIME PMFD FIRST DAY OF MONTH LESS 1 MONTH STARTING TODAY
   GENTIME PMLD LAST DAY OF MONTH LESS 30 DAYS STARTING TODAY
   ECHO !PMFDMM!PMFDDD!PMFDYEAR !PMLDMM!PMLDDD!PMLDYEAR
   RUN 3RD WORKDAY OF APR JUN SEP NOV
ENDJOB

AIX_JOB GENTIME_28_DAY_MONTH LINK PROCESS
   GENTIME PMFD FIRST DAY OF MONTH LESS 1 MONTH STARTING TODAY
   GENTIME PMLD LAST DAY OF MONTH LESS 28 DAYS STARTING TODAY
   ECHO  !PMFDMM!PMFDDD!PMFDYEAR !PMLDMM!PMLDDD!PMLDYEAR
   RUN 3RD WORKDAY OF FEB
   NORUN FEB 3 2016
   NORUN FEB 5 2020
   NORUN FEB 5 2024
   NORUN FEB 3 2028
   DELAYSUB 12.00
ENDJOB

AIX_JOB GENTIME_29_DAY_MONTH LINK PROCESS
   GENTIME PMFD FIRST DAY OF MONTH LESS 1 MONTH STARTING TODAY
   GENTIME PMLD LAST DAY OF MONTH LESS 29 DAYS STARTING TODAY
   ECHO !PMFDMM!PMFDDD!PMFDYEAR !PMLDMM!PMLDDD!PMLDYEAR
   RUN FEB 3 2016
   RUN FEB 5 2020
   RUN FEB 5 2024
   RUN FEB 3 2028
   DELAYSUB 12.00
ENDJOB

